这个神殿不只是凡人的双手堆起来的
This temple is not just bricks and mortar

24
00:00:57,529 --> 00:01:00,364
砖头和灰泥
built by the hands of men.

25
00:01:00,399 --> 00:01:03,200
这是神在人间的屋子
It is the house of God on earth,

26
00:01:03,235 --> 00:01:05,469
他的家
his home,

27
00:01:05,504 --> 00:01:07,838
最神圣的地方
the Holy of Holies.

